                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 9.178,
                                "byte_start": 77440,
                                "byte_stop": 114220,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in Eddings against Oklahoma will be announced by Justice Powell."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.178,
                        "stop": 192.903,
                        "byte_start": 114220,
                        "byte_stop": 849097,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15119,
                            "name": "Lewis F. Powell, Jr.",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/lewis_f_powell_jr",
                            "last_name": "Powell",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2764,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 63612000,
                                    "date_end": 551682000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2764"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32738,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 53543,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/lewis_f_powell_jr.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 5649,
                            "identifier": "lewis_f_powell_jr"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 9.178,
                                "stop": 17.926,
                                "byte_start": 114220,
                                "byte_stop": 149224,
                                "text": "This is a capital case here on certiorari to the Court of Appeals -- Court of Criminal Appeals of Oklahoma."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 17.926,
                                "stop": 33.478,
                                "byte_start": 149224,
                                "byte_stop": 211396,
                                "text": "When Eddings was 16 years old, he shot and killed a state highway patrol officer at the time Eddings, with three younger juveniles, was running away from their Missouri homes."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 33.478,
                                "stop": 51.064,
                                "byte_start": 211396,
                                "byte_stop": 281718,
                                "text": "He had a history of emotional problems, had been raised in a difficult family situation, and there was testimony that his mental and emotional development were at a level several years below his chronological age."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 51.064,
                                "stop": 64.376,
                                "byte_start": 281718,
                                "byte_stop": 335007,
                                "text": "The Oklahoma capital punishment statute provides in the sentencing proceeding that evidence may be presented as to mitigating and aggravating circumstances."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 64.376,
                                "stop": 90.01,
                                "byte_start": 335007,
                                "byte_stop": 437512,
                                "text": "Eddings\u0027 age was considered as a mitigating circumstance but this was viewed as outweighed by aggravating circumstances primarily the deliberate shooting of a state officer without provocation other than the fact that Eddings have been stopped on a state highway for erratic driving."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 90.01,
                                "stop": 104.285,
                                "byte_start": 437512,
                                "byte_stop": 494668,
                                "text": "Although the trial court admitted evidence as to Eddings\u0027 family history and emotional instability, it declined to consider these as mitigating circumstances."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 104.285,
                                "stop": 110.085,
                                "byte_start": 494668,
                                "byte_stop": 517864,
                                "text": "The Court of Criminal Appeals agreed and a sentence of death was affirmed."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 110.085,
                                "stop": 130.537,
                                "byte_start": 517864,
                                "byte_stop": 599680,
                                "text": "In Lockett against Ohio, we held that the Eighth and Fourteenth Amendments require in a capital case that the sentencing authority not be precluded from considering, as a mitigating factor, any aspect of a defendant\u0027s character or record."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 130.537,
                                "stop": 140.196,
                                "byte_start": 599680,
                                "byte_stop": 638237,
                                "text": "We think the Oklahoma Court\u0027s committed error in failing to consider Eddings\u0027 background in mitigation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 140.196,
                                "stop": 150.047,
                                "byte_start": 638237,
                                "byte_stop": 677629,
                                "text": "We therefore reverse the judgment insofar as it imposed the death penalty and remand the case for further proceedings."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 150.047,
                                "stop": 165.788,
                                "byte_start": 677629,
                                "byte_stop": 740637,
                                "text": "This Court is not unaware of the extent of which minors engage increasingly in violent crime nor do we suggest an absence of legal responsibility where crime is committed by a minor."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 165.788,
                                "stop": 178.721,
                                "byte_start": 740637,
                                "byte_stop": 792359,
                                "text": "We are concerned in this case only with the validity of the procedure by which the death sentence was imposed on an emotionally disturbed 16-year-old."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 178.721,
                                "stop": 183.728,
                                "byte_start": 792359,
                                "byte_stop": 812421,
                                "text": "Justices Brennan and O\u0027Connor have filed concurring opinions."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 183.728,
                                "stop": 192.903,
                                "byte_start": 812421,
                                "byte_stop": 849097,
                                "text": "The Chief Justice has filed a dissenting opinion in which Justices White, Blackmun, and Rehnquist have joined."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
